WEBVTT

1
00:00:11.390 --> 00:00:13.000
That was my stomach, sorry.

2
00:00:14.430 --> 00:00:16.510
What's your name?

3
00:00:17.550 --> 00:00:18.690
Denji!

4
00:00:18.690 --> 00:00:21.010
Let me be perfectly clear.

5
00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:25.770
From now on, you will be my dog.

6
00:00:26.430 --> 00:00:28.740
You may only answer me with "yes" or "woof."

7
00:00:28.740 --> 00:00:30.760
I have no use for a dog that says "no."

8
00:00:32.030 --> 00:00:33.530
What do you mean?

9
00:00:33.530 --> 00:00:36.280
I heard from a friend in Forensics

10
00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:41.030
that we euthanize dogs that are no longer useful.

11
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:48.620
I thought she was kind.

12
00:00:49.110 --> 00:00:51.310
I fell for her a bit.

13
00:00:51.310 --> 00:00:54.170
I had no idea she was such a scary woman.

14
00:00:54.170 --> 00:00:56.880
She treats people like dogs.

15
00:01:02.750 --> 00:01:05.350
That's right. Pochita's dead.

16
00:01:09.660 --> 00:01:12.290
We haven't had breakfast yet, either.

17
00:01:12.290 --> 00:01:14.650
Let's get something at the rest stop.

18
00:01:15.060 --> 00:01:17.900
Sorry, but I'm flat broke.

19
00:01:18.260 --> 00:01:20.020
Just tell me what you want.

20
00:01:20.020 --> 00:01:21.690
It's my treat.

21
00:01:23.170 --> 00:01:25.910
You'll draw too much attention if you're half-naked, so take this.

22
00:01:28.880 --> 00:01:29.560
Here.

23
00:01:35.410 --> 00:01:39.600
My whole life, people have called me dirty and smelly and avoided me.

24
00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:41.930
No one's ever treated me so kindly before.

25
00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:44.630
Certainly not a girl as pretty as her.

26
00:01:48.050 --> 00:01:49.260
I'm in love.

27
00:01:53.290 --> 00:01:55.760
Oh, I'd like some udon and...

28
00:01:55.760 --> 00:01:58.590
Udon and... a hot dog!

29
00:01:58.590 --> 00:01:59.640
If that's all right?

30
00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:00.770
Sure.

31
00:02:00.770 --> 00:02:02.860
And a curry udon for me.

32
00:02:02.860 --> 00:02:04.020
Coming right up.

33
00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:07.200
Ah, curry udon sound goo—

34
00:02:07.520 --> 00:02:08.700
Oh, hello.

35
00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:10.720
Denji?

36
00:02:10.720 --> 00:02:11.700
Are you okay?

37
00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:12.790
Um...

38
00:02:12.790 --> 00:02:14.540
Smells good...

39
00:02:14.540 --> 00:02:15.940
How much is that?

40
00:02:15.940 --> 00:02:17.670
Just a moment.

41
00:02:16.530 --> 00:02:17.670
Denji.

42
00:02:18.210 --> 00:02:19.800
I'm sorry.

43
00:02:18.210 --> 00:02:19.800
That'll be 1,300 yen.

44
00:02:22.910 --> 00:02:24.220
Here. Keep the change.

45
00:02:19.800 --> 00:02:22.910
The chainsaws cut me up as well.

46
00:02:22.910 --> 00:02:26.210
I must've lost a little too much blood.

47
00:02:26.810 --> 00:02:29.220
How did you become like this?

48
00:02:29.750 --> 00:02:32.970
My pet devil became my heart.

49
00:02:34.090 --> 00:02:35.720
Hard to believe, I know.

50
00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.450
I don't want to believe it either.

51
00:02:38.450 --> 00:02:41.270
Pochita gave his life to save me...

52
00:02:45.770 --> 00:02:50.490
Your condition is almost without precedent.

53
00:02:51.220 --> 00:02:54.240
In fact, it's so uncommon that there's no word for it.

54
00:02:55.830 --> 00:02:58.190
I believe you, though.

55
00:03:00.150 --> 00:03:03.000
I have an especially keen sense of smell.

56
00:03:03.520 --> 00:03:04.740
That's why I can tell.

57
00:03:06.100 --> 00:03:09.090
Your friend is alive inside of you.

58
00:03:09.420 --> 00:03:11.220
And I don't mean that in any poetic sense.

59
00:03:11.670 --> 00:03:15.480
Your body gives off both the scent of a human and that of a devil.

60
00:03:16.530 --> 00:03:17.730
Really?

61
00:03:17.730 --> 00:03:18.980
Wow.

62
00:03:18.980 --> 00:03:21.340
I'm so hap—

63
00:03:29.140 --> 00:03:29.880
Udon!

64
00:03:31.800 --> 00:03:32.500
Udon?

65
00:03:39.000 --> 00:03:41.120
Can I eat my udon now?

66
00:03:41.460 --> 00:03:42.130
Yeah.

67
00:03:42.650 --> 00:03:44.130
Are sure you're okay?

68
00:03:44.130 --> 00:03:45.380
Can you eat it on your own?

69
00:03:45.380 --> 00:03:46.460
I ca—

70
00:03:48.410 --> 00:03:49.880
I can't.

71
00:03:50.180 --> 00:03:52.160
Say, "Ah!"

72
00:03:52.160 --> 00:03:53.130
Ah!

73
00:03:55.110 --> 00:03:56.100
Do you like it?

74
00:03:56.100 --> 00:03:56.890
Woof!

75
00:03:57.260 --> 00:04:00.380
Most people would turn their nose up at soggy udon.

76
00:04:00.380 --> 00:04:02.140
What a good boy you are.

77
00:04:02.430 --> 00:04:04.020
You really are quite like a dog.

78
00:04:07.470 --> 00:04:10.350
So, what's your name?

79
00:04:11.710 --> 00:04:12.650
Makima.

80
00:04:13.070 --> 00:04:14.200
Makima?

81
00:04:14.650 --> 00:04:18.140
D-Do you have a type when it comes to men?

82
00:04:18.140 --> 00:04:19.660
Hmm...

83
00:04:24.760 --> 00:04:27.090
Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.

84
00:04:27.990 --> 00:04:29.110
Denji?

85
00:04:30.660 --> 00:04:31.310
Huh?

86
00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:33.740
Me?

87
00:04:42.690 --> 00:04:45.440
Do you have a type when it comes to men?

88
00:04:45.440 --> 00:04:47.020
Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.

89
00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:47.110
Someone like this Denji guy, I'd say.

90
00:04:49.590 --> 00:04:52.490
I love you too, Makima.

91
00:04:54.220 --> 00:04:55.300
Denji!

92
00:04:55.300 --> 00:04:56.650
This way!

93
00:04:59.010 --> 00:05:01.810
This is the Tokyo HQ for the Bureau's devil hunters.

94
00:05:06.350 --> 00:05:11.530
If you include civilians, there are over a thousand devil hunters in Tokyo,

95
00:05:11.530 --> 00:05:15.920
but the Bureau offers a lot of paid vacation time and the best benefits by far.

96
00:05:19.290 --> 00:05:22.270
If Makima's into me,

97
00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:26.790
then there's a chance we could become a couple if we keep working together.

98
00:05:27.770 --> 00:05:29.770
And if we become a couple,

99
00:05:29.770 --> 00:05:32.530
we can do couple things together.

100
00:05:32.530 --> 00:05:33.560
I wanna do it so bad!

101
00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.780
I wanna do the thing that couples do!

102
00:05:38.770 --> 00:05:40.030
Denji.

103
00:05:40.450 --> 00:05:41.280
Yes?

104
00:05:42.030 --> 00:05:44.790
We have a uniform, so put this on.

105
00:05:45.310 --> 00:05:47.910
Once you've changed, I'll introduce you to one of your coworkers.

106
00:05:55.710 --> 00:05:58.340
This is Hayakawa Aki.

107
00:05:58.340 --> 00:06:00.600
He's been working here for three years.

108
00:06:01.150 --> 00:06:03.610
Tag along with him for the day.

109
00:06:03.610 --> 00:06:04.100
Huh?!

110
00:06:04.650 --> 00:06:07.330
I'm not going to work with you?!

111
00:06:07.860 --> 00:06:09.350
Of course you're not.

112
00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:12.430
You're nowhere near her league.

113
00:06:12.430 --> 00:06:13.430
We're going out on patrol.

114
00:06:13.430 --> 00:06:14.380
No!

115
00:06:14.380 --> 00:06:16.110
Makima!

116
00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.550
Hey! Get up!

117
00:06:18.550 --> 00:06:19.660
No way!

118
00:06:19.660 --> 00:06:22.100
I wanna work with Makima.

119
00:06:24.850 --> 00:06:27.390
You could work with me,

120
00:06:27.390 --> 00:06:29.220
if you can prove you can do a good job.

121
00:06:38.230 --> 00:06:40.130
So show me what you can do, okay?

122
00:06:47.730 --> 00:06:49.640
Hey, Aki.

123
00:06:50.220 --> 00:06:52.650
Does Makima have a boyfriend?

124
00:06:56.500 --> 00:06:57.510
Hello?

125
00:06:59.580 --> 00:07:00.030
Tell me!

126
00:07:01.150 --> 00:07:02.280
Come with me.

127
00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:29.640
Quit this job.

128
00:07:30.730 --> 00:07:33.040
If you show up tomorrow, 
I'll beat the crap out of you again.

129
00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:34.900
Why?

130
00:07:36.180 --> 00:07:38.650
Can't you see I'm doing you a favor?

131
00:07:39.360 --> 00:07:42.330
If you're not serious about this job, 
you'll be dead in no time.

132
00:07:42.330 --> 00:07:46.410
Everyone I've worked with who came for the paycheck is now dead.

133
00:07:46.410 --> 00:07:48.660
Killed by devils, all of them.

134
00:07:49.290 --> 00:07:53.400
The only ones who're still alive are those with deep convictions.

135
00:07:54.590 --> 00:07:55.610
And let me guess...

136
00:07:56.210 --> 00:07:58.800
You only took this job to get close to Makima, right?

137
00:07:59.130 --> 00:08:00.720
Bingo.

138
00:08:01.630 --> 00:08:04.220
Then I was right to beat you up.

139
00:08:08.560 --> 00:08:10.920
I'll explain things to Makima.

140
00:08:11.390 --> 00:08:14.080
How you got scared of a devil and ran away.

141
00:08:28.640 --> 00:08:31.910
You're too nice, man.

142
00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:36.670
When I fight a dude,

143
00:08:36.920 --> 00:08:40.160
I only go for the balls!

144
00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:49.980
Today, I ate udon for the first time.

145
00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:52.810
And a hot dog too.

146
00:08:52.810 --> 00:08:55.390
I was treated like a person for the first time.

147
00:08:55.390 --> 00:08:57.680
Someone bought me a meal for the first time.

148
00:08:58.320 --> 00:09:01.190
To me, this is like a dream come true.

149
00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:05.950
I'm not very serious about being a devil hunter. You're right.

150
00:09:06.360 --> 00:09:08.820
But if it means I can keep living like this,

151
00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:11.250
I don't even care if it gets me killed.

152
00:09:12.870 --> 00:09:14.850
Actually, I take that back.

153
00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:17.580
This life isn't just mine anymore.

154
00:09:22.820 --> 00:09:24.220
You want Makima?

155
00:09:25.170 --> 00:09:29.640
No way she'd fall for a lowlife like you.

156
00:09:29.640 --> 00:09:30.390
What?!

157
00:09:30.630 --> 00:09:31.640
Screw you!

158
00:09:31.640 --> 00:09:34.560
You just have a thing for her too!

159
00:09:39.790 --> 00:09:42.360
You really do...

160
00:09:43.590 --> 00:09:45.730
only go for...

161
00:09:45.730 --> 00:09:47.860
the balls...

162
00:09:53.460 --> 00:09:54.790
Shit.

163
00:09:56.910 --> 00:10:00.630
The Balls Devil got his balls.

164
00:10:01.170 --> 00:10:02.440
That's a lie.

165
00:10:02.440 --> 00:10:04.170
He's lying.

166
00:10:04.450 --> 00:10:06.670
Okay, what do you think?

167
00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:08.680
Can you two work together?

168
00:10:08.680 --> 00:10:09.710
No freakin' way.

169
00:10:09.710 --> 00:10:11.300
He's total scum.

170
00:10:11.570 --> 00:10:13.860
I'm glad to see you're getting along.

171
00:10:14.590 --> 00:10:17.560
Denji, you will be joining Hayakawa's unit.

172
00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:18.870
Unit?

173
00:10:18.870 --> 00:10:20.810
This lowlife?!

174
00:10:20.810 --> 00:10:24.270
We already have enough troublemakers as it is.

175
00:10:24.270 --> 00:10:26.430
We can't afford to take any more weirdos.

176
00:10:26.430 --> 00:10:29.090
Remember what I told you when I formed the unit?

177
00:10:29.090 --> 00:10:33.190
It's meant to be experimental, rather than conform to standards and conventions.

178
00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:38.080
Who is this guy, anyway?

179
00:10:38.360 --> 00:10:42.310
He's a human, but he can also turn into a devil.

180
00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:44.350
You gotta admit, pretty awesome, hey?!

181
00:10:44.350 --> 00:10:46.200
You're not pulling my leg, are you?

182
00:10:46.200 --> 00:10:50.420
I've only heard vague rumors about such a thing.

183
00:10:50.420 --> 00:10:52.720
Denji is special.

184
00:10:53.330 --> 00:10:57.980
So he's getting special treatment.

185
00:10:58.260 --> 00:11:02.090
If he quits the Bureau or commits any offense,

186
00:11:02.090 --> 00:11:05.070
he will be treated as a devil and eliminated.

187
00:11:05.910 --> 00:11:06.730
Huh?

188
00:11:07.180 --> 00:11:09.990
What do you mean?

189
00:11:10.560 --> 00:11:13.540
I mean that we'll be working together until the day you die.

190
00:11:17.400 --> 00:11:20.500
It was decided that you'll live with me 
so I can keep an eye on you.

191
00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:24.500
And don't forget, I have permission to kill you if you run away.

192
00:11:31.180 --> 00:11:34.260
So, do you think Makima is a bad person?

193
00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:37.390
If you think she is, then give up on her.

194
00:11:37.790 --> 00:11:39.510
If you're a devil,

195
00:11:39.510 --> 00:11:41.390
just be grateful she's letting you live.

196
00:11:41.880 --> 00:11:44.400
After all, we're devil hunters.

197
00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:46.800
So, is she a good person?

198
00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:48.440
Of course she is.

199
00:11:49.970 --> 00:11:52.410
She saved my life.

200
00:12:02.350 --> 00:12:03.960
Makima...

201
00:12:04.590 --> 00:12:06.800
I wanna feel her warm embrace again.

202
00:12:07.270 --> 00:12:08.710
What?!

203
00:12:08.710 --> 00:12:08.800
What?!

204
00:12:10.800 --> 00:12:14.800
Strawberry jam, ume jam, orange marmalade,

205
00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:18.270
butter and honey, and...

206
00:12:18.270 --> 00:12:20.560
I'll throw some cinnamon on too.

207
00:12:20.810 --> 00:12:23.810
This is now the ultimate slice of toast.

208
00:12:26.610 --> 00:12:27.940
Hell yeah!

209
00:12:29.010 --> 00:12:31.190
Sooo freakin' good!

210
00:12:41.220 --> 00:12:42.370
Don't stay in there too long!

211
00:12:44.990 --> 00:12:46.830
Don't sleep on the toilet!

212
00:12:57.140 --> 00:12:59.600
A fiend has been sighted at a residential building in west Nerima.

213
00:13:00.430 --> 00:13:02.170
All civilians have been evacuated,

214
00:13:02.170 --> 00:13:04.350
and a perimeter has been established.

215
00:13:05.010 --> 00:13:08.370
The target fiend is holed up in a room on the second floor.

216
00:13:08.370 --> 00:13:10.430
We'll let you guys take it from here.

217
00:13:10.430 --> 00:13:13.360
Hayakawa, is that a new recruit you've got there?

218
00:13:17.900 --> 00:13:19.870
By the way, what's a fiend?

219
00:13:20.190 --> 00:13:23.670
What? Did you not go to school or something?

220
00:13:23.670 --> 00:13:25.410
No, actually.

221
00:13:27.530 --> 00:13:31.230
A devil that has taken over a human's corpse—that's a fiend.

222
00:13:31.230 --> 00:13:32.280
Hmm...

223
00:13:33.680 --> 00:13:36.210
Wait, does that mean I'm a fiend too?

224
00:13:36.210 --> 00:13:39.890
You can easily recognize a fiend by how their head looks.

225
00:13:40.180 --> 00:13:42.890
You'll understand when you see it.

226
00:13:49.750 --> 00:13:51.990
A fiend still has the character of a devil.

227
00:13:51.990 --> 00:13:53.860
You kill this one.

228
00:13:54.380 --> 00:13:56.490
Turn into a devil, and show me what you've got.

229
00:13:56.830 --> 00:13:59.310
Then I'll decide if you can be useful or not.

230
00:13:59.860 --> 00:14:01.240
Don't look!

231
00:14:01.490 --> 00:14:04.240
You're dead! Dead! Dead!

232
00:14:04.240 --> 00:14:06.250
You filthy devil hunters!

233
00:14:14.440 --> 00:14:17.970
Hold on, why didn't you use your devil powers?

234
00:14:18.220 --> 00:14:23.140
Well, when I use my power to kill devils,

235
00:14:23.140 --> 00:14:24.720
it looks really painful.

236
00:14:25.010 --> 00:14:30.980
You see, I could've ended up a fiend like him,

237
00:14:31.400 --> 00:14:35.360
so... I kinda wanted to give him a quick and painless death.

238
00:14:36.990 --> 00:14:38.660
Listen here, punk.

239
00:14:39.200 --> 00:14:40.950
A fiend is still a devil.

240
00:14:41.450 --> 00:14:43.870
As a devil hunter, you shouldn't show them any sympathy.

241
00:14:44.470 --> 00:14:48.120
My entire family was killed by a devil, 
right before my eyes.

242
00:14:48.900 --> 00:14:51.950
I've been out drinking with some of those cops downstairs.

243
00:14:51.950 --> 00:14:55.630
They put their lives on the line, 
all to protect their wives and children.

244
00:14:56.370 --> 00:14:58.620
You're the only one here who's not taking this seriously.

245
00:14:59.120 --> 00:15:02.640
I want to kill devils in the most painful way possible.

246
00:15:03.330 --> 00:15:04.530
And you?

247
00:15:04.530 --> 00:15:06.890
You want to be friends with them?

248
00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:11.400
Sure, if there's a devil who wants to be my friend, I'm down.

249
00:15:12.700 --> 00:15:14.450
After all, I don't have any friends.

250
00:15:18.820 --> 00:15:21.380
I'm going to remember you said that.

251
00:15:30.460 --> 00:15:32.420
Man, that made him snap.

252
00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:36.200
I actually just didn't wanna get blood on these porno mags.

253
00:15:36.670 --> 00:15:40.430
If I brought the chainsaws out, they'd be soaked right now.

254
00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:44.470
In return for giving you a quick death, 
I'm taking these, all right?

255
00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:50.760
Sweet!

256
00:15:50.760 --> 00:15:51.940
It's the good stuff.

257
00:15:52.450 --> 00:15:55.230
Let me see your dreams come true.

258
00:15:55.540 --> 00:15:58.480
I'm serious too, Pochita.

259
00:15:58.930 --> 00:16:02.240
I'm living out my dreams, just like our contract says.

260
00:16:02.870 --> 00:16:04.990
I'm going to remember you said that.

261
00:16:05.510 --> 00:16:08.910
My dreams have already come true,

262
00:16:08.910 --> 00:16:10.750
but he's still chasing his.

263
00:16:13.290 --> 00:16:15.410
I can take a bath every day.

264
00:16:15.410 --> 00:16:17.080
I can eat good stuff.

265
00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:19.380
I have a pretty girl near me.

266
00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:22.050
My life's already 10 outta 10.

267
00:16:22.550 --> 00:16:24.490
Even so, it feels like something's missing.

268
00:16:24.930 --> 00:16:28.390
Do I have something else? Like a serious goal?

269
00:16:28.690 --> 00:16:31.450
For him, it must be something to do with revenge.

270
00:16:31.450 --> 00:16:33.650
For those guys, it's to protect their families.

271
00:16:36.760 --> 00:16:38.830
I wonder if Makima has something like that.

272
00:16:39.890 --> 00:16:41.400
Makima...

273
00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:45.660
Boobs! I wanna touch some boobs!

274
00:16:51.490 --> 00:16:54.780
I gave up a long time ago, 
'cause I didn't have a chance in hell.

275
00:16:54.780 --> 00:16:58.040
But now that I've got proper a job, 
it's a different story.

276
00:16:58.780 --> 00:17:01.580
My chances of going all the way are still slim, though,

277
00:17:02.270 --> 00:17:03.550
but if it's just boobs...

278
00:17:04.600 --> 00:17:07.930
With a little confidence and determination, 
I could be fondling boobs.

279
00:17:08.400 --> 00:17:10.730
You're the only one here who's not taking this seriously.

280
00:17:10.730 --> 00:17:12.430
Now I get it.

281
00:17:13.240 --> 00:17:15.980
I found the thing that'll push me to be serious!

282
00:17:16.350 --> 00:17:18.130
My goal!

283
00:17:18.130 --> 00:17:19.230
It's...

284
00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:20.730
boobs!

285
00:17:21.230 --> 00:17:22.360
Boobs?

286
00:17:22.620 --> 00:17:25.230
Hey! Pay attention, moron!

287
00:17:25.230 --> 00:17:26.110
What?

288
00:17:26.390 --> 00:17:29.620
I am assigning you a partner, starting now.

289
00:17:30.140 --> 00:17:31.270
A partner?

290
00:17:31.270 --> 00:17:34.250
The Bureau's rules are that for small-scale missions and patrols,

291
00:17:34.570 --> 00:17:39.000
agents must work in teams of two, 
for safety reasons.

292
00:17:39.540 --> 00:17:42.130
Great timing. That's her now.

293
00:17:43.270 --> 00:17:44.910
Be careful, though.

294
00:17:44.910 --> 00:17:46.260
She's a fiend.

295
00:17:47.730 --> 00:17:48.980
Listen here!

296
00:17:48.980 --> 00:17:50.520
Prostrate yourself before me, human!

297
00:17:50.520 --> 00:17:52.400
My name is Power!

298
00:17:52.400 --> 00:17:54.410
Are you to be my partner?

299
00:17:55.420 --> 00:17:57.530
Power? Your name's "Power"?!

300
00:17:57.530 --> 00:17:58.770
And you're a fiend?!

301
00:17:59.340 --> 00:18:02.210
Is a fiend really working as a devil hunter?!

302
00:18:05.560 --> 00:18:06.930
Ah, what the hell.

303
00:18:06.930 --> 00:18:08.190
Let's work together!

304
00:18:09.280 --> 00:18:12.540
Under normal circumstances, 
fiends are to be eliminated just like devils,

305
00:18:12.820 --> 00:18:15.130
but Power is rather reasonable,

306
00:18:15.130 --> 00:18:17.290
so I had her join Hayakawa's unit.

307
00:18:17.890 --> 00:18:19.490
As I mentioned before,

308
00:18:19.490 --> 00:18:22.900
the Public Safety Bureau's Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division is an experimental unit.

309
00:18:23.320 --> 00:18:28.550
The higher-ups could disband it at any time, 
if it doesn't produce results.

310
00:18:28.910 --> 00:18:32.800
And you know what would happen to the two of you then, right?

311
00:18:39.080 --> 00:18:41.810
Power's horns stand out,

312
00:18:41.810 --> 00:18:45.070
so only patrol in areas where there are few people around.

313
00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:58.460
Human! Hurry up and find me something to kill!

314
00:18:58.460 --> 00:19:00.800
I thirst for blood!

315
00:19:03.710 --> 00:19:07.720
I can forgive some amount of annoyingness for a pretty face.

316
00:19:08.770 --> 00:19:11.720
But how do I touch her boobs?

317
00:19:14.330 --> 00:19:16.980
If you run into any civilian devil hunters

318
00:19:16.980 --> 00:19:20.230
or police officers wanting to question you, then if you say...

319
00:19:18.130 --> 00:19:20.230
Approaching suspicious individuals.

320
00:19:18.130 --> 00:19:20.230
You two, come over here for a minute.

321
00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:23.480
Public Safety Bureau, 
Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division.

322
00:19:23.480 --> 00:19:25.460
and show them your badge,

323
00:19:25.460 --> 00:19:27.450
they'll walk away in a huff and leave you alone.

324
00:19:30.500 --> 00:19:32.450
There's no freakin' devils here!

325
00:19:32.700 --> 00:19:35.660
Probably my fault.

326
00:19:35.660 --> 00:19:39.710
Before I became a fiend, 
I was a much-feared devil.

327
00:19:40.340 --> 00:19:43.290
Small fry flee the moment they catch a whiff of my scent.

328
00:19:43.290 --> 00:19:46.090
Wait, what?! How're we supposed to deliver results, then?!

329
00:19:47.580 --> 00:19:50.970
If you have any questions, direct them to Hayakawa.

330
00:19:51.730 --> 00:19:53.720
He's the one who decided to partner you two up.

331
00:19:54.130 --> 00:19:57.100
That bastard set me up!

332
00:19:57.560 --> 00:20:00.560
He stuck me with Power so I won't have a chance to show 'em what I can do.

333
00:20:00.560 --> 00:20:03.100
He's trying to make me quit!

334
00:20:06.260 --> 00:20:07.980
That's the smell of blood!

335
00:20:09.690 --> 00:20:11.270
Hey, wait a sec!

336
00:20:11.270 --> 00:20:12.200
Where're you going?

337
00:20:16.030 --> 00:20:18.200
A fight! A fight!

338
00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:20.070
To battle!

339
00:20:20.070 --> 00:20:21.040
Damn, she's quick!

340
00:20:21.310 --> 00:20:24.790
Civilians have been evacuated, 
and a perimeter's been established.

341
00:20:25.090 --> 00:20:27.670
It's the Sea Cucumber Devil. 
I repeat, the Sea Cucumber Devil.

342
00:20:27.930 --> 00:20:30.410
Requesting backup at Nerima Station.

343
00:20:30.410 --> 00:20:32.500
No, I said sea cucumber.

344
00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:34.390
You know what a sea cucumber is, right?

345
00:20:34.390 --> 00:20:36.830
What? No, I told you—

346
00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:43.020
Sea cucumber...

347
00:20:43.420 --> 00:20:44.770
Behold!

348
00:20:45.030 --> 00:20:47.010
My accomplishment!

